summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over portions of Block 53, Burke's 2nd Addition (Lake Washington-Central, Contract 5-1, Sewer Improvement); over a portion of Government Lot 2, in the northwest one-quarter of Section 10, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. (Lake Washington-Central, Contract 5-B, Sewer Improvement); and over a portion of 26th Avenue South as vacated (Ord. 86558) (Neighborhood Improvement Project, Contract 6; Sewer Improvement) for storm drain purposes.
